  "content": "<p data-pid=\"ry51442x\">转载自 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/Colerar\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Colerar</a> 翻译、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Piotr_Wozniak\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">彼得 · 沃兹尼亚克</a>所著的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/Colerar/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《睡眠好，学习好，生活好》</a>，这里是译文目录和翻译的话。</p><h2>翻译的话</h2><p data-pid=\"GBYTPULS\">本翻译以 Markdown 语言写成，并导出成 HTML PDF PNG 等格式。推荐您使用 HTML 格式以获得最佳体验。</p><p data-pid=\"u_l-_yL9\">翻译并非 100% 准确。但我保证在我能力范围之内提供最好的翻译。如果您觉得有所讹误，可以提交 Issue，或者直接提交 PR。</p><p data-pid=\"X4rbT2lq\">对于英文 Wikipedia 链接，将替换或添加为对应中文 Wikipedia 链接（若有），并适当新增了外链。关于术语，请参见<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23glossary\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">术语</a>一节。</p><p data-pid=\"gG4H5y9z\">译者推荐您先阅读<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23incremental_writing\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">增量写作</a>一节，再看一下<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23references\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">参考</a>和<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23glossary\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">术语</a>前的声明。浏览<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23content\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">目录</a>后，根据您的喜好，选读<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23summary\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">概要</a>和<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">正文</a>。您不必一天全部读完，也不必按顺序读，有兴趣的时候再读也无妨。</p><p data-pid=\"RedYTQPN\">最后，感谢 Piotr Woźniak 博士在学习、记忆、睡眠方面的贡献。谢谢你！</p><h2>目录</h2><ol><li data-pid=\"NIPtEPpu\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/496140203\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">介绍</a></li><li data-pid=\"RfVhwxB3\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/496742631\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">睡眠的重要性</a></li><li data-pid=\"wzchqWWX\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/497000116\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">为什么要睡觉？</a></li><li data-pid=\"xcfPici8\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/497975420\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">睡眠剥夺是致命的</a></li><li data-pid=\"E5a1JNZ_\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/497982235\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">生物钟和恒常性睡意</a></li><li data-pid=\"74ctftlv\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/497982873\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">优质睡眠公式</a></li><li data-pid=\"ySGjJGUg\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/497983631\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">睡眠习惯</a></li><li data-pid=\"Mv9PzOUC\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/720533648\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">双相的生活</a></li><li data-pid=\"kllH5n_j\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/786275878\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">脑力劳动的最佳时间</a></li><li data-pid=\"1FiQbcKo\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/547116585\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">闹钟</a></li><li data-pid=\"RyTUZ8fG\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/583611918\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">健康的午睡</a></li><li data-pid=\"mS4qUxT0\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/3054777168\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">午睡的最佳时机</a></li><li data-pid=\"jgy0uoGg\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/606888160\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">小睡谬误</a></li><li data-pid=\"cV7VBHiY\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/15175221691\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">影响睡眠的因素</a></li><li data-pid=\"1BwI3JT4\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1897966540843914066\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">15 我们应该睡多长时间？</a></li><li data-pid=\"nc4uk6U9\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1915483653053617542\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">婴儿睡眠</a></li><li data-pid=\"l4rugQ9q\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1920870897704736060\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">失眠</a></li><li data-pid=\"yTFk-xh0\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1925596544150804041\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">睡眠惯性</a></li><li data-pid=\"mgTmdFrL\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1935996086130053136\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">轮班工作与时差反应</a></li><li data-pid=\"Z85-w1zz\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1936366484105454872\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">睡眠呼吸暂停</a></li><li data-pid=\"OpUzKUYP\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1939270209425903857\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">嗜睡症</a></li><li data-pid=\"mJm8k-2J\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1951939573891438395\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">睡眠相位后移综合征</a></li><li data-pid=\"k2CDu1eH\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1953783256492273745\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">睡眠相位前移综合征</a></li><li data-pid=\"VY1Cw_bP\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1975173357847720709\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">治疗睡眠相位延迟综合征与失眠</a></li><li data-pid=\"LjWOd1Iu\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1980280587588769288\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">绘制相位变化图</a></li><li data-pid=\"XWEektr0\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23Segmented_sleep\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Segmented sleep</a></li><li data-pid=\"WNLtx8Tv\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23Function_of_sleep\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Function of sleep</a></li><li data-pid=\"tPN5voBa\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23Sleep_and_learning\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Sleep and learning</a></li><li data-pid=\"xTrtfHgR\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23How_do_we_fall_asleep%3F\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">How do we fall asleep?</a></li><li data-pid=\"2IcHlnjV\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23NREM_sleep_and_REM_sleep\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">NREM sleep and REM sleep</a></li><li data-pid=\"mo2SlM-B\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23Neural_optimization_in_sleep\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Neural optimization in sleep</a></li><li data-pid=\"EexGGYyH\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23Scientists_who_contest_memory_optimization\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Scientists who contest memory optimization</a></li><li data-pid=\"DhgM227i\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Good_sleep%2C_good_learning%2C_good_life%23Circadian_oscillator_genes\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Circadian oscillator genes</a></li><li data-pid=\"GNs7cp8J\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/497990585\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">传闻和事实</a></li><li data-pid=\"qxpvPcyJ\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/497994260\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">概要</a></li></ol><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"ihKcxWcK\">题图：桃とシャミ子 by Tsugu_0928 <br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//colerar.github.io/Chinese-Translation-Good-sleep-good-learning-good-life/%23content\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">翻译-睡眠好，学习好，生活好 (colerar.github.io)</a> by <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/Colerar\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Colerar</a></blockquote>",
